41
00:01:32,310 --> 00:01:34,650
Thinking about this helps
you make better decisions

42
00:01:34,650 --> 00:01:36,720
about how you use your resources.

43
00:01:36,720 --> 00:01:39,270
I'm not saying I always
make the right decisions

44
00:01:39,270 --> 00:01:41,520
but on average, I've come out profitable

45
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:43,020
