123
00:04:43,410 --> 00:04:45,120
I speak from experience.

124
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:47,541
I made a few lucky
investments in penny stocks

125
00:04:47,541 --> 00:04:48,960
when I was younger,

126
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:50,880
and had I continued on that path,

127
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:52,650
I would've lost everything.

128
00:04:52,650 --> 00:04:55,530
To be more exact, I had
the opportunity to invest

129
00:04:55,530 --> 00:04:58,410
in a big group with a couple
of billionaire friends.

130
00:04:58,410 --> 00:05:01,110
Everything they touched,
seemed to turn to gold.

131
00:05:01,110 --> 00:05:03,540
