132
00:05:03,540 --> 00:05:06,570
but they had investments
in fashion, retail,

133
00:05:06,570 --> 00:05:08,310
and big banks everywhere.

134
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,200
I didn't really understand
how they were seeing

135
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:14,520
