lost over $300,000

140
00:05:25,860 --> 00:05:29,700
because they were leveraging
every investment by six times,

141
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:32,490
which led to this whole
operation going bankrupt.

142
00:05:32,490 --> 00:05:34,080
It's a good lesson to learn though

143
00:05:34,080 --> 00:05:35,850
because I would've previously thought

144
00:05:35,850 --> 00:05:37,530
that the amount that I'd invested

145
00:05:37,530 --> 00:05:40,170
