while I was still young,

173
00:06:43,890 --> 00:06:45,112
not wait until I was older

174
00:06:45,112 --> 00:06:48,030
to finally reap the
benefits of my investments.

175
00:06:48,030 --> 00:06:49,500
That's why it's so important

176
00:06:49,500 --> 00:06:51,930
to learn some kind of high income skill

177
00:06:51,930 --> 00:06:54,660
