radio control helicopters.

180
00:06:59,160 --> 00:07:02,370
I developed a skill that
not many people could master

181
00:07:02,370 --> 00:07:05,190
so I charged people to pass on that skill.

182
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:07,710
The money I earned was in
addition to what I needed

183
00:07:07,710 --> 00:07:09,360
for my normal expenses

184
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:12,360
so it became money that
I could easily invest.

185
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,970
It's essential to have
another stream of income

186
00:07:14,970 --> 00:07:18,240
and a side hustle is a
really great way to do that.

187
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,250
Now, if you lose your main job,

188
00:07:20,250 --> 00:07:23,310
you still have the source of
income to invest gradually

189
00:07:23,310 --> 00:07:25,920
