and affiliate marketing.

195
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,150
Here's an idea.

196
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:41,310
Look at what you do in your normal job.

197
00:07:41,310 --> 00:07:44,010
Can you transfer this to a side hustle?

198
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:45,360
It doesn't matter what you do.

199
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:48,150
From an electrician to a forklift driver,

200
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:51,030
you can find a way to turn
it into a side hustle.

201
00:07:51,030 --> 00:07:54,210
