225
00:08:49,020 --> 00:08:50,790
I thought how great it was.

226
00:08:50,790 --> 00:08:53,250
A hammer's a hammer, a chisel's a chisel.

227
00:08:53,250 --> 00:08:54,960
What difference could there be?

228
00:08:54,960 --> 00:08:57,240
And these were better than half price.

229
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,587
I bought a bunch of these tools

230
00:08:58,587 --> 00:09:00,420
and I took them back to work.

231
00:09:00,420 --> 00:09:01,380
But to my dismay,

232
00:09:01,380 --> 00:09:04,020
the hammer shaft bent almost immediately.

233
00:09:04,020 --> 00:09:06,960
The chisels didn't stay
sharp for more than a minute,

234
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,670
and the screwdrivers,

235
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,890
