244
00:09:27,810 --> 00:09:30,600
Living a better life
changes you as a person,

245
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,790
it makes you more comfortable socializing

246
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:34,860
with high net worth people

247
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,480
as you don't feel like a fraud.

248
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:40,770
Spending less, of course, is
a good idea in some situations

249
00:09:40,770 --> 00:09:43,770
